          { speaker: 'b', speakerName: 'James', en: 'That feels convincing to me. It suggests the routine is not just comforting; it is actually reshaping your way of meeting reality.', zh: '我喜歡這種衡量方式，因為它在乎的是穩定，不是表演。' }
